channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/33mwufb.jpg[/img] Well, ive decided to release since i will be moving back to 317's and a 508 im working on with my buddy RuneWings317, i havent had anytime to host any servers and this was the plan with this server, so for now im just doing projects and coding them. Well yeah, all the information +updates can be found here. http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,541475.0.html well heres a list i guess to what the server has
Its a 667 loading 711.
all the skills are working, trading is fixed as well. I added some cool talking npcs to bring you around to cool places. i deleted crappy Mr Ex and replaced it with using the teletab instead as i find that a more efficient way of teleport. There a shit load of others, so yeah check it out. Download - removed due to fag leechers client - leechers
some media - [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/21awcg7.png[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/16m60i1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2zoexef.png[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/686j2a.png[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/4k8xvq.png[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/35jgxa1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/33uso6b.png[/img] and before you say "oh you leeched shabba's source and client" well i basically deleted most of shabba's stuff so i dont really care what you call me, this source isnt finished just didnt feel like hosting :P
some features - added pk point shop added Pk drop system fixed trade Portals donating sytem new skilling area started soul wars uhh fixed some stats for items voting rewards
uhm idk if this is the new source, i just picked the one in my public dropbox so yeh...\
creds Kronixz (me) Cj Ash Shabba 56 (most creds to him) do not release on any other sites please. or i will slam ur muff.
